text.autoconfig.pretty-hitboxes.title: Pretty Hitboxes
text.autoconfig.pretty-hitboxes.option.h: Enables hitboxes when the game starts, so you don't have to enable them manually
Hides the lage box around the dragon that isn't actually it's hitbox
text.autoconfig.pretty-hitboxes.option.d: Change Bounding Box Color on Target
Changes the color of an entity's bounding box when they are targeted and in hitting range
text.autoconfig.pretty-hitboxes.option.s: Shows or hides hitboxes for item entities
Shows or hides hitboxes for item frames specifically
Shows or hides hitboxes for thrown items (pearls, eggs, snowballs)
text.autoconfig.pretty-hitboxes.option.b: Red value of the color's RGB value. Should be a number between 0 and 255, inclusive. Smaller or large values will be clamped.
